        <abstract> 
<p>CD offers to mark corrected passages in sheets of 6th edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p>  
<p>Discusses question of hybrids between goats and sheep, on which H. von Nathusius has cast doubt in his recent <hi rend="italic">Viehzucht</hi> [1872]. CD gives several references for a contrary view.</p> 
            <p>Asks JVC to inquire about HvN’s assertion that castrated rams have no horns.</p>
        </abstract>
